#: .\Ammo\Arrows.json
msgid "experimental smart arrow"
msgid_plural "experimental smart arrows"
msgstr[0] ""
msgstr[1] ""

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'experimental smart arrow'}
#: .\Ammo\Arrows.json
msgid ""
"This experimental arrow is equipped with active stabilization and targeting "
"systems for perfect accuracy, even when hitting small or moving targets. "
"While only decently damaging, this arrow was designed for special forces "
"when stealth is necessary. A simple teleport system even returns the arrow "
"to the user after firing."
msgstr ""

#: .\Ammo\Bolts.json
